        <h2>Oilfield Housing FAQ</h2>
        <div class="gline"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Does Best Western Vernal offer housing for oilfield workers? <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. We regularly house oilfield workers, pipeline crews, drilling teams, and energy contractors working in the Uintah Basin. We offer weekly and monthly rates, truck parking, corporate billing, and the full amenity package.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Is there truck and equipment parking on site? <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. We have on-site parking suitable for work trucks, trailers, and larger vehicles. This is a standard expectation for our oilfield and contractor guests.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Can my company set up a billing account for the crew? <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. We work with companies to set up corporate accounts with invoicing and itemized billing. Call us at <a href="tel:4357896625">(435) 789-6625</a> to discuss your company's needs before the crew arrives.</p></div></div>
