        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Can workers on rotating schedules share the same company account? <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. We can manage rotating personnel under a single company account. Workers check in and out as the rotation changes, with billing consolidated at the company level.</p></div></div>
        <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q">Is there laundry available for field crews? <span class="faq-arrow">▼</span></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Yes. Washer and dryer facilities are available on property. For crews going back into the field, end-of-week laundry is straightforward without leaving the hotel.</p></div></div>
